Name: Average resolution time following 'Accepted + Wait - Customer'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Customer and the end of the case

Name: Median duration from 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Longest duration from 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' to 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The maximum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Shortest duration from 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' to any subsequent activity
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Customer and the end of the case

Name: Average duration from 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' to 'Accepted + In Progress'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Total duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Customer and the end of the case

Name: Average waiting time before 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' is initiated
Metric: The average of the duration between the start of the case and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer'

Name: Duration variance of 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' to 'Completed + Closed'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Time difference between 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' in the same case
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'

Name: Earliest start time of 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' after 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer'

Name: Latest finish time of 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' before 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The maximum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Average duration from 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' to the next activity, grouped by country
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and the end of case grouped by the last value of organization country

Name: Total count of transitions from 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' to 'Accepted + In Progress' across all variants
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Average duration from 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' to 'Completed + In Call' in the most frequent variant
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Duration from the first occurrence of 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' to the last occurrence in each case
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer'

Name: Time until first occurrence of 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' from case start
Metric: The average of the duration between the start of the case and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer'

Name: Time from 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' to case closure
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Comparison of average duration from 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' to 'Completed + In Call' versus 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Maximum duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' in any given process variant
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and the last time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x000001E27CECF0A0> - AppliesTo.PROCESS

Name: Minimum time gap between 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and any 'Completed' activity
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Customer' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'
